        <trans-unit id="8c9fee72c5f2cfd8616dd20d0d6e90683f071bfd" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>In the end, however, I would second &lt;a href=&quot;https://faq.cprogramming.com/cgi-bin/smartfaq.cgi?answer=1352443831&amp;amp;id=1043284392&quot;&gt;the FAQ's last option&lt;/a&gt;:</source>
          <target state="translated">&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Al final, sin embargo, apoyar&amp;iacute;a &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://faq.cprogramming.com/cgi-bin/smartfaq.cgi?answer=1352443831&amp;amp;id=1043284392&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;la &amp;uacute;ltima opci&amp;oacute;n de las preguntas frecuentes&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; :&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;</target>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="761e1e531d5379ce8ff1bd64d090ba4983f59ccc" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Is that right?</source>
          <target state="translated">¿Es eso cierto?</target>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="4f94e199059b049ac1280e4330baba0b53592ad0" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Note that non-whitespace &quot;directives&quot; (to use &lt;a href=&quot;http://pubs.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/9699919799/functions/scanf.html&quot;&gt;POSIX scanf terminology&lt;/a&gt;) other than conversions, like the literal text in &lt;code&gt;scanf(&quot;order = %d&quot;, &amp;amp;order);&lt;/code&gt; doesn't skip whitespace either.  The literal &lt;code&gt;order&lt;/code&gt; has to match the next character to be read.</source>
          <target state="translated">&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Tenga en cuenta que las &quot;directivas&quot; que no son espacios en blanco (para usar la &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://pubs.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/9699919799/functions/scanf.html&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;terminolog&amp;iacute;a POSIX scanf&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; ) que no sean conversiones, como el texto literal en &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &lt;code&gt;scanf(&quot;order = %d&quot;, &amp;amp;order);&lt;/code&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;tampoco se salta el espacio en blanco. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;El &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &lt;code&gt;order&lt;/code&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; literal &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;tiene que coincidir con el siguiente car&amp;aacute;cter a leer.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;</target>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="724e7966571c209b3e01084023429cabcc8f5ad9" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Note that this still doesn't consume any trailing whitespace left in the input stream, not even to the end of a line, so beware of that if also using &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.cppreference.com/w/c/io/getchar&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;getchar()&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.cppreference.com/w/c/io/fgets&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;fgets()&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; on the same input stream.  We're just getting scanf to skip over whitespace &lt;em&gt;before&lt;/em&gt; conversions, like it does for &lt;code&gt;%d&lt;/code&gt; and other non-character conversions.</source>
          <target state="translated">&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Tenga en cuenta que esto todav&amp;iacute;a no consume ning&amp;uacute;n espacio en blanco al final de la secuencia de entrada, ni siquiera al final de una l&amp;iacute;nea, as&amp;iacute; que tenga cuidado con eso si tambi&amp;eacute;n usa &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://en.cppreference.com/w/c/io/getchar&quot;&gt; &lt;code&gt;getchar()&lt;/code&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; o &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://en.cppreference.com/w/c/io/fgets&quot;&gt; &lt;code&gt;fgets()&lt;/code&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; en la misma secuencia de entrada. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Solo estamos haciendo que scanf omita el espacio en blanco &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;antes de las&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; conversiones, como sucede con &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &lt;code&gt;%d&lt;/code&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; otras conversiones que no son de caracteres.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;</target>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="66a0938676e71d234343b452186d8c4dabcb624d" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Or, depending on your requirements, you could also forget about scanf()/getchar(), use fgets() to get a line of text from the user and parse it yourself.</source>
          <target state="translated">O,dependiendo de tus necesidades,también podrías olvidarte de scanf()getchar(),usar fgets()para obtener una línea de texto del usuario y analizarla tú mismo.</target>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="3d7f898e9536b25b8fae927214a88358936787a1" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>So you probably want &lt;code&gt;&quot; order = %d&quot;&lt;/code&gt; there if you want to skip a newline from the previous line but still require a literal match on a fixed string, &lt;a href=&quot;https://stackoverflow.com/questions/49923312/scanf-run-twice-instead-of-one-time-at-assembly-x86-64&quot;&gt;like this question&lt;/a&gt;.</source>
          <target state="translated">&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Por lo tanto, probablemente desee &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &lt;code&gt;&quot; order = %d&quot;&lt;/code&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; all&amp;iacute; si desea omitir una nueva l&amp;iacute;nea de la l&amp;iacute;nea anterior pero a&amp;uacute;n as&amp;iacute; requiere una coincidencia literal en una cadena fija, &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://stackoverflow.com/questions/49923312/scanf-run-twice-instead-of-one-time-at-assembly-x86-64&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;como esta pregunta&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; .&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;</target>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="3c00448b2e4fd712712cda090d3c14cda6d3142b" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>The &lt;a href=&quot;http://pubs.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/9699919799/functions/scanf.html&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;scanf()&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; function skips leading whitespace automatically before trying to parse conversions other than characters.  The character formats (primarily &lt;code&gt;%c&lt;/code&gt;; also scan sets &lt;code&gt;%[&amp;hellip;]&lt;/code&gt; &amp;mdash; and &lt;code&gt;%n&lt;/code&gt;) are the exception; they don't skip whitespace.</source>
          <target state="translated">&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;La funci&amp;oacute;n &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://pubs.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/9699919799/functions/scanf.html&quot;&gt; &lt;code&gt;scanf()&lt;/code&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; omite los espacios en blanco iniciales autom&amp;aacute;ticamente antes de intentar analizar conversiones que no sean caracteres. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Los formatos de caracteres (principalmente &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &lt;code&gt;%c&lt;/code&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; ; tambi&amp;eacute;n conjuntos de escaneo &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &lt;code&gt;%[&amp;hellip;]&lt;/code&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; - y &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &lt;code&gt;%n&lt;/code&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; ) son la excepci&amp;oacute;n; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;No se saltan los espacios en blanco.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;</target>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="646a629b1c7bd53cfa549e3b4607aecb21fd6ab0" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Use &lt;code&gt;&quot; %c&quot;&lt;/code&gt; with a leading blank to skip optional white space.  Do not use a trailing blank in a &lt;code&gt;scanf()&lt;/code&gt; format string.</source>
          <target state="translated">&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Use &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &lt;code&gt;&quot; %c&quot;&lt;/code&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; con un espacio en blanco inicial para omitir el espacio en blanco opcional. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;No utilice un espacio en blanco final en una &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;cadena de formato &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &lt;code&gt;scanf()&lt;/code&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; .&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;</target>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="9b2af5c9e78f20f0c0b651f3c3b40d58f355fbbb" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Use &lt;code&gt;getchar()&lt;/code&gt; before calling second &lt;code&gt;scanf()&lt;/code&gt;.</source>
          <target state="translated">&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Use &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &lt;code&gt;getchar()&lt;/code&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; antes de llamar al segundo &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &lt;code&gt;scanf()&lt;/code&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt; .&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;</target>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="5bc4388c0d38b4213c63476101d6b199eab0366d" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Use &lt;code&gt;scanf(&quot; %c&quot;, &amp;amp;c2);&lt;/code&gt;. This will solve your problem.</source>
          <target state="translated">&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Use &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt; &lt;code&gt;scanf(&quot; %c&quot;, &amp;amp;c2);&lt;/code&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Esto resolver&amp;aacute; su problema.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;</target>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="a657963f850559de4877656311a7b69804613b50" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>scanf() leaves the new line char in the buffer</source>
          <target state="translated">scanf()deja la nueva línea de caracteres en el buffer</target>
        </trans-unit>
